snippet.title: Lost Soul Aside PSX 2017 Special Demo OP
snippet.description:
OP of the Lost Soul Aside PSX 2017 special demo.
Game under development does not represent final quality.
All footages in the video are captured in the playable demo in PSX 2017 event.
Check more information at: https://www.facebook.com/lostsoulaside/
Music composed by Adam Bow ( https://soundcloud.com/bowadam ).
